racelets as a home remedy to possibly ease the pain from arthritis in some people who seem to get an insufficient amount of copper from their food. \n\nFinally be careful because not all products in the market are authentic, always make sure it has the Sabona trademark on it. There is a fake product sold but is spelt saponah.', 0.6369888186454773, 1, 500, '2025-09-16 08:15:10.446668', '2025-09-16 08:15:10.446668');
