INSERT INTO public.responses (question_id, question_text, llm_response, original_answer, bert_score, processing_attempts, total_processing_time_ms, created_at, updated_at) VALUES ('81ff8bb51f251d85', 'why do people let gender-discrimination continue to happen in the military?', 'Persiste por la **cultura militar tradicional** y **resistencia al cambio**, las **jerarqu├¡as de poder establecidas**, las **percepciones hist├│ricas** sobre los roles de g├⌐nero, y la **falta de rendici├│n de cuentas** efectiva.', 'Women are playing a big role in the War in Iraq. I think it is entirely possible for women to serve in the Infantry and other Combat Arms occupations simply because of what they have done so far in the current war. In todays kind of guerilla warfare it is actually more likely that a truck driver or other non combat arms occupation will be attacked than the infantry. This is because the Infantry train so well  and so often that the insurgents can''''t match up against them. Once they learn this they begin to target military units who do not train for combat as much as combat arms occupations. These are the type of units that women are allowed to take part in and consequently they often times see combat. Now the US Army is beginning to train all MOS (Military Occupation Specialties) for combat almost as much as the soldiers whos sole occupation is combat.\n\nWomen will probably experience some sort of discrimination for a long time simply because of tradition gender role stereotypes. However, eventually I think official policy will change to put women on the same level as men in most aspects of the military.', 0.5865347385406494, 1, 500, '2025-09-16 18:04:20.081538', '2025-09-16 18:04:20.081538');
INSERT INTO public.responses (question_id, question_text, llm_response, original_answer, bert_score, processing_attempts, total_processing_time_ms, created_at, updated_at) VALUES ('db8bf72972dad013', 'How does culture reflect the economic and social organization of a people?', 'La cultura **encarna los valores, normas y creencias** que una sociedad desarrolla para **organizar su producci├│n, distribuci├│n y relaciones interpersonales.** Refleja sus **estructuras de poder, jerarqu├¡as y la forma en que interact├║a con sus recursos y entorno.**', 'This orientation has allowed him to explore and advocate some quite ΓÇÿutopianΓÇÖ and abstract ideas (especially around systems theory and the necessity of bringing human values to the workplace). At the same time he has been able to mediate these so that they can be worked on and applied by people in very different forms of organization. His areas of special interest are said to focus on decentralizing the role of leadership in organizations so as to enhance the capacity of all people to work productively toward common goals. One aspect of this is SengeΓÇÖs involvement in the Society for Organizational Learning (SoL), a Cambridge-based, non-profit membership organization. Peter Senge is its chair and co-founder. SoL is part of a ΓÇÿglobal community of corporations, researchers, and consultantsΓÇÖ dedicated to discovering, integrating, and implementing ΓÇÿtheories and practices for the interdependent development of people and their institutionsΓÇÖ. One of the interesting aspects of the Center (and linked to the theme of idealistic pragmatism) has been its ability to attract corporate sponsorship to fund pilot programmes that carry within them relatively idealistic concerns.', 0.6243505477905273, 1, 500, '2025-09-16 18:04:22.867696', '2025-09-16 18:04:22.867696');
INSERT INTO public.responses (question_id, question_text, llm_response, original_answer, bert_score, processing_attempts, total_processing_time_ms, created_at, updated_at) VALUES ('f6b3272411fd4391', 'Why stomach making sound when we feel hungry?', 'Son las **contracciones musculares** (peristalsis) del est├│mago e intestinos moviendo aire y l├¡quidos. Cuando est├ín vac├¡os y sin alimento que amortig├╝e el sonido, este se hace audible.', 'Your stomach makes noises because your it is contracting and trying to digest but all that is in there is your gastric juices, it''''s kind of like squsihing a water ballon that is only a little bit full', 0.6182565093040466, 1, 500, '2025-09-16 18:04:31.277138', '2025-09-16 18:04:31.277138');
